Due to official budgetary restrictions, we have to place a deadline on
requests for funding from students who wish to attend the Makkaifest
18 - 20 June 2009 in Montreal.

   http://www.crm.umontreal.ca/Makkaifest09/index_e.php

Any requests received after midnight (GMT) Monday 15 June will have to
be refused.  Students wishing to apply for funding should register on
the meeting homepage, and fill out the funding request to be found
there.  (Funding is limited, and will only be "partial" - anyone
wanting more information is invited to email me directly.)

